                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-249-victim1316 t18270215-249-viclabel1337"></join>, and live in Wood-street, in partnership with Stephen and Edward Wilson. On the 20th of January the prisoner came and presented this order to me, saying he came from Mrs. Badham, for two black silk handkerchiefs - I gave him two in consequence of this order. (Read.)</p>
               <p>Please send by bearer two black silk handkerchiefs, large size, for Mrs. Badham, 20th of January, 1827.</p>
